title: 05/13/21 DPS Hour 3 Mina Kimes

description:
Mina Kimes tells Dan that she believes that the QB winner of the Super Bowl will be younger than 33 years old. Mina says she is surprised that the NFL schedule did not include more Browns and Chargers games on national television.
